Name: Spirit Overflow
About the game: In Spirit Overflow, players compete in teams for territory and challenge other riders in online multiplayer battles. Â Every match is an intense 3v3 battle that calls for skills, strategies and sweat. Capture your territory You will leave a trail after your character, when the trail forms a closed shape, you can capture a territory. When time is up, the team with more territory wins the game. Use randomly generated items Items will randomly appear in the arena which gives you a certain power-up, including healing, speed boost, and damage. Use them properly will give you the advantage over the opponents. Ultimate skill Activate your ultimate skill and hit your enemy! it can instantly kill an enemy. Play alone or build your squad Spirit Overflow is a team-based game where team strategy is essential to the victory. Like any other e-sport, you'll be able to create or join a team and play together with your squad. Bring your friends, party up, and build the strongest team! *rendered video, in-game visual work in progress
